topic.title: Do you know Alldebrid service
topic.body:
Have a look at: www.alldebrid.com 
Once you created an account and paid for a period, you will be able to debrid nearly any kind of links and enjoy the downloads without time to wait: mega, uptobox, uploaded, rapidgator and so on..
There's another great thing. In the torrent section, you will be able to add several torrent files or a magnet link, and the site will download for you. When downloads are completed, it will give a Uptobox link. 
Behind the scene, the website stores the files already downloaded. So, when you will insert a magnet or a torrent file to download, you may not have to wait, if the same content has been downloaded before ;)
Enjoy ;)
